node.text:
I CAN’T STRESS THIS ENOUGH: START TAKING CARE OF YOURSELF. ⁣⁣
⁣
Taking care of yourself is an act of SELF-LOVE. Want to be happy? Successful? Wealthy? It all starts with you.⁣
⁣
With your choices and your actions. ⁣
⁣
The good thing is you don't have to keep living in a way that’s unhealthy for you and your loved ones. ⁣
⁣
You can make a change by choosing to take care of YOURSELF. ⁣
⁣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '12 Laws of Karma'.
Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 1. The Great Law. Whatever we put into the universe will come back to us.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 2. The Law of Creation. Life does not happen by itself, we need to make it happen. 3. The Law of Humility. One must accept something in order to change it.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 4. The Law of Growth. When we change ourselves, our lives follow suit and change too. 5. The Law of Responsibility We must take responsibility for what is in our lives.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 6. The Law Law of Connection. The past, present and future are all connected. 7. The Law of Focus. We cannot think of two different things at the same time.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 8. The Law of Giving and Hospitality Our behavior should match our thoughts and actions. 9. The Law of Here and How. We cannot be present if we are looking backward.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 10. 10. The Law of Change. History repeats itself until we learn from it and change our path. 11. The Law of Patience and Reward The most valuable rewards require persistence.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '12 Laws of Karma 12. The Law of Significance and Inspiration Rewards are a result of the energy and effort we put into it. Tag a friend who should see this!'.
Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'IF YOU WANT TO BECOME SUCCESSFUL THEN YOU SHOULD READ THIS SHORT CAPTION FOR 1 MINUTE...'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Maturity is When someone hurts you and you try to understand their situation, instead of nstear hurting them back.'.
Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 07, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'If you could see what's what's COMING, you wouldn't stress about what's happening.'.

Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Let being at peace be more important than making a point.'.
Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You are the greatest project you will ever work on. @BUSINESSMINDSETI01'.
Photo by BusinessMindset101®️ on August 03, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'Treat yourself like someone you love At the end of the day you are with youse the longest.'.
